data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom CBS construction home nestled in the desirable northeast area of Ocala! Discover the allure of a spacious yard, complemented by a convenient small metal workshop, offering endless possibilities for hobbyists. With a garage ingeniously converted into additional living space, this residence showcases versatility and functionality. Moreover, rest assured with peace of mind knowing that this residence features a recently updated HVAC system and duct work, ensuring comfort and reliability for years to come. Inside, revel in the comfort of a split-bedroom floor plan, ensuring privacy and relaxation for all. While showcasing its inherent charm, this lovely home also presents a canvas for personalization, offering the opportunity for small renovations to tailor the space to your unique vision and preferences. Don't miss the opportunity to experience charm and practicality in this delightful Ocala home!
